text: numbala aturinma numbalata upamavak ohu gena hæra penviya. api numbalata posanaya kala dæhi havulkaruvan kisiveku ho numbalage dakunat himikaragat aya aturin numbalata vet da? numbala ehi samanada? numbala atara numbala biyavannak men numbala ovunata da biyavannehuya. vataha ganna janayata ema vadan api pæhædili karanuye elesaya
